|description2 = The song "Si Veo a Tu Mamá" from his album ''[[YHLQMDLG]]'' samples the bossa nova standard "[[The Girl from Ipanema]]" by [[Antônio Carlos Jobim]]<ref name=siveobillboard>{{cite magazine|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/latin/9333551/bad-bunny-si-veo-a-tu-mama-lyric-translation-english|title=Bad Bunny's 'Si Veo A Tu Mama' Is For Everyone Who's Not Over Their Ex: Lyric Translation|magazine=[[Billboard (magazine)|Billboard]]|last=Roiz|first=Jessica|date=March 12, 2020|access-date=May 6, 2020}}</ref> and features Bad Bunny alternating between rapping and singing.
